The purpose of the Data Scientist is to analyze large amounts of data that help us make smarter decisions to deliver even better solutions.
Our ideal candidate for this role should have a good background as a Data Scientist and critical thinking and problem-solving skills for interpreting data.
If this opportunity is for you, apply today!

We will rely on you to:
- Identify valuable data sources and automate collection processes;
