Our client is a top-tier data engineering firm, specialized in Spark and many other distributed technologies for almost a decade. It operates in a remote-first culture and with an international mindset.

Benefits

It is not only THE most interesting firm operating in Big Data in Italy in terms of projects and skills they can teach, but it is also among those offering the best benefits and perks to its employees, such as
Remote working or Smart working from one of its offices (up to the employee);
It offers the chance to work remotely from a chosen location, for a few weeks every year (usually a sunny beach in Spain) ALL PAID BY THE COMPANY;
Public handbook and policy, that everyone can check on their website, making them among the most transparent and honest employees in Italy;
