Deep knowledge of Flutter SDK and Dart;
Understanding of Reactive Programming, BLoC and Streams;
Abilities to use Swift or Kotlin are considered an advantage;
A good understanding of integration and deployment processes for mobile applications;
Professional, precise communication skills;
