Creating self-contained, reusable, and testable modules and components;
A good understanding of the application development lifecycle as well as UI/UX concepts;
Lifelong learning mindset and open to exploring and working with different technologies;
Stay up to date with best programming practices and new tech trends;
Very good command of spoken and written English.

